# Exercise 000 - Exposing your application

1) Deploy again your mysql application, this time without removing the
   Service part

2) Verify if the DeploymentConfig, Pods and Service are up&running

3) Check if mysql is reachable (either with just a netcat) from
   inside and outside the OpenShift Cluster

4) Delete the service

5) Create a new NodePort service, mapping port 30003

6) Verify the status and the service object

7) Verify the Service yaml

8) Check if mysql is reachable (either with just a netcat) from
   inside and outside the OpenShift Cluster
